                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div id="w-node-_13aad53d-6d2c-6d26-094c-f2b8b79290a5-34f3a516" class="color-card">
                      <div class="color-block neutral-800"></div>
                      <div class="color-details-block">
                        <div class="color-heading">Neutral 800</div>
                        <p class="color-code">#1d1d1d</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div id="w-node-_06186a91-ca32-2900-768a-e1e6f85a4896-34f3a516" class="color-card">
                      <div class="color-block black-color"></div>
                      <div class="color-details-block">
                        <div class="color-heading">Black color</div>
                        <p class="color-code">#000000</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div id="w-node-_17ef72cf-3899-60d5-43bf-daf3d078d40b-34f3a516" class="color-card">
                      <div class="color-block red-500"></div>
                      <div class="color-details-block">
                        <div class="color-heading">Red 500</div>
                        <p class="color-code">#d0473e</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div id="w-node-df80a25e-bbe8-07b8-62e8-0e543f5c5d19-34f3a516" class="color-card">
                      <div class="color-block green-500"></div>
                      <div class="color-details-block">
                        <div class="color-heading">Green 500</div>
                        <p class="color-code">#14854e</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Typography -->
              <div id="typography" class="typography-wrapper">
                <div class="style-guide-heading-wrapper">
                  <h2 class="style-guide-heading">Typography</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="typography-details-wrapper">
                  <div class="typography-details-block">
                    <h1 class="large-title">Display 1</h1>
                    <p class="style-guide-short-info">Large Title - 80px /112.5/% || Bold || Instrument Sans<br /></p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="typography-details-block">
                    <h1>Heading 1</h1>
                    <p class="style-guide-short-info">H1 - 64px /112.5/% || Bold || Instrument Sans<br /></p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="typography-details-block">
                    <h2>Heading 2</h2>
                    <p class="style-guide-short-info">H2 - 48px /115/% || Semi Bold || Instrument Sans<br /></p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="typography-details-block">
                    <h3>Heading 3</h3>
                    <p class="style-guide-short-info">H3 - 40px /120/% || Medium || Instrument Sans<br /></p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="typography-details-block">
                    <h4>Heading 4</h4>
                    <p class="style-guide-short-info">H4 - 24px /120/% || Medium || Instrument Sans<br /></p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="typography-details-block">
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Suspendisse varius enim in eros elementum tristique. Duis cursus, mi quis viverra ornare, eros dolor interdum nulla, ut commodo diam libero vitae erat. Aenean faucibus nibh et justo cursus id rutrum lorem imperdiet. Nunc ut sem vitae risus tristique posuere.</p>
                    <p class="style-guide-short-info">Paragraph - 16px /162.5% || Regular || Inter</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="typography-details-block">
                    <p class="large-paragraph">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Suspendisse varius enim in eros elementum tristique. Duis cursus, mi quis viverra ornare, eros dolor interdum nulla, ut commodo diam libero vitae erat. Aenean faucibus nibh et justo cursus id rutrum lorem imperdiet. Nunc ut sem vitae risus tristique posuere.</p>
                    <p class="style-guide-short-info">Large Paragraph - 18px /155.5% || Regular || Inter</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="typography-details-block">
                    <p class="small-paragraph">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Suspendisse varius enim in eros elementum tristique. Duis cursus, mi quis viverra ornare, eros dolor interdum nulla, ut commodo diam libero vitae erat. Aenean faucibus nibh et justo cursus id rutrum lorem imperdiet. Nunc ut sem vitae risus tristique posuere.</p>
                    <p class="style-guide-short-info">Small Paragraph - 14px /162.5% || Regular || Inter</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="typography-details-block">
                    <blockquote>"Embrace each moment with courage and determination, for it is through challenges that we grow. Remember, success is not measured by the absence of obstacles, but by the strength to overcome them."</blockquote>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Buttons -->
              <div id="buttons" class="style-guide-button-wrapper">
                <div class="style-guide-heading-wrapper">
                  <h2 class="style-guide-heading">Buttons</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="style-guide-button-block">
                  <a href="#" class="primary-button w-inline-block">
                    <div class="button-text-block">
                      <div class="button-text">Button Text</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="button-bg"></div>
                  </a>
                  <a href="#" class="secondary-button w-inline-block">
                    <div class="button-text-block">
                      <div class="button-text">Button Text</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="button-bg secondary"></div>
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Icons -->
              <div id="Icons" class="style-guide-icon-wrapper">
                <div class="style-guide-heading-wrapper">
                  <h2 class="style-guide-heading">Icons</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="style-guide-icon-block">
                  <img loading="lazy" src="/images/search.svg" alt="Style Guide Icon" class="style-guide-icon" />
                  <img loading="lazy" src="/images/user-icon.svg" alt="Style Guide Icon" class="style-guide-icon" />
                  <img loading="lazy" src="/images/footer-icon-1.svg" alt="Style Guide Icon" class="style-guide-icon" />
                  <img loading="lazy" src="/images/footer-icon-3.svg" alt="Style Guide Icon" class="style-guide-icon" />
                  <img loading="lazy" src="/images/footer-icon-2.svg" alt="Style Guide Icon" class="style-guide-icon" />
                  <img loading="lazy" src="/images/feature-icon-1.svg" alt="Style Guide Icon" class="style-guide-icon" />
                  <img loading="lazy" src="/images/feature-icon-3.svg" alt="Style Guide Icon" class="style-guide-icon" />
                  <img loading="lazy" src="/images/feature-icon-2.svg" alt="Style Guide Icon" class="style-guide-icon" />
